    <item>
      <title>电子巨头富士康进军电动汽车领域，实现业务多元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/electronics-giant-foxconn-looks-to-diversify-with-ev-foray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾工业巨头富士康正在台北举办年度科技日。该公司正式名称为鸿海，是全球最大的电子产品代工制造商。现在，该公司面临着多元化发展和建立更具未来保障的收入来源的需求。我们的科技记者 Annabelle Droulers 展望了未来的机遇和挑战。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/electronics-giant-foxconn-looks-to-diversify-with-ev-foray</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假期过后中国股市飙升，市场热情持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过一周的假期后，随着交易的恢复，在岸上市的中国股票大幅上涨，令人鼓舞的房屋销售和消费数据为北京刺激计划引发的股市上涨提供了新的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-stocks-surge-on-return-from-holidays-as-euphoria-extends</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克·莫比乌斯认为中国股市因经济增长支持而有更多上涨空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/mark-mobius-sees-more-upside-for-china-stocks-on-growth-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·莫比乌斯表示，如果政策制定者继续推出支持市场的措施，中国股市的上涨趋势可能会持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/mark-mobius-sees-more-upside-for-china-stocks-on-growth-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假期过后，中国主权债券延续刺激措施引发的低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-sovereign-bonds-extend-stimulus-led-slump-after-holidays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期北京的刺激计划可能会延续历史性的股市反弹，对避险资产的需求下降，中国政府债券在一周假期后恢复交易后下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-sovereign-bonds-extend-stimulus-led-slump-after-holidays</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 01:14:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pictet 文件错误地显示了 150 亿美元的中国银行押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/pictet-filing-mistakenly-showed-15-billion-bet-on-chinese-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据这家瑞士资产管理公司称，一份香港交易所文件错误地显示，百达资产管理公司向中国建设银行股份有限公司投资了 1212 亿港元（156 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/pictet-filing-mistakenly-showed-15-billion-bet-on-chinese-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行暗示维持基准利率直至对价格有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/rba-signals-key-rate-to-stay-at-4-35-until-confident-on-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上次董事会会议记录显示，澳大利亚央行将维持利率在当前的 12 年来的最高水平，直到确信通胀率可持续地向其目标区间移动，这表明政策放松仍有一段距离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/rba-signals-key-rate-to-stay-at-4-35-until-confident-on-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
